cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image classification using a neural network architecture that involves wavelet transforms and parametric log transformations. This is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) research. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of unsupervised methods (cs.NE) and compares the proposed network to other supervised methods (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates the computational efficiency of the network (cs.MM).
